data.description: Discover comfort and charm in this lovely two-story residence located in the desirable Weston Ranch Community. This spacious home offers ample space for both relaxation and entertaining. Downstairs bedroom. Beat the Stockton heat with your own pool, perfect for enjoying sunny California days. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this home offers close proximity to the esteemed Great Valley Elementary School, shopping amenities, and easy access to Highway 5. A little tender loving care can unveil the hidden potential within this home. Currently Tenant-occupied.
